    Product description

    Specification:

    • Power: 5W
    • Input Voltage: 110V-130V AC
    • Emitting Color: RGB & CCT 2700-6500K Color Changing
    • Dimmable: Dimmable
    • Brightness: 350LM
    • Material Type: Aluminum + Flame Retardant PC
    • Front Diameter: 70mm/2.75inch
    • Cutout Opening Diamerter: 53mm/2.08 inch
    • Height: 34.8mm/1.37 inch

    Package includes:

    • 4 x 3W Dimmable Smart LED Recessed Lighting


    Voice Control

    Control your smart lightings via your voice with Alexa, Google Assistant and so on. Just give a voice command to turn on/off or adujst the brintness of your smart lights.


    APP Control

    Control your smart downlights with your phone through Smart Life App. Creat scenes, time nodes, colors anywhere anytime.


    Devices Sharing

    Share devices with your families or friends! (Authorization is needed by the devices owner). Why not try a wake up color notice for your relatives or love ones, or a dim bedtime story call for your childs.

    1%-100% adjustable brightness, 16 million changable colors, 2700-6500K dimmable color temprature. Perfect choice for most spots.

    Group set mode: through the establishment of group set, you can manage your lights as you want. ONE CLICK to control all your smart lights! Single Light on/off and color switching, or choosen multiple lights on/off and color switching, NO MORE DIMMER ON WALL.

    Timing mode: set mutiple time nodes for smart lights to turn on/off automatically.

    Music mode: Enter the music mode, which the color of smart lights will change with the music rhythm. Make your home a perfect meditation room to rest, or a club for you and your friends, it is all decided by you!

    Scenes Function: There are 8 scene modes, you can customize the lighting scenes any time, anywhere, in any combination!

    Installation Steps

    1. Drill a hole 2.2"(56mm) in size.

    2. Connect the wires for recessed lighting.

    3. Twist both spring clips upwards and push into the hole.

    4. push the spring clips and the light affix to the mounting hole.

    Connect Wifi downlights with Smart Life APP

    Turn on/off the switch 3 times continuously to enter pairing mode( the light will flash). Choose your smart lighting devices on SmartLife APP, pair the light-app-wifi up under auto instruction, and enjoy the SMART LIFE!

    Note:

    Only compatible with 2.4GHz network, 5GHz network is not supported.

    The light can only be dimmed by App & voice control, not compatible with the DIMMER switch.

    Connection with Alexa

    Download and register your account on Smart Life APP.

    Please rename the lights with an easy name for easier voice control via Alexa or other voice assistant.

    APP Load

    Maximum time nodes per device: 30.

    Maximum decives under a "familiy": 200.

    Maximum sence under a "family": 100.

    Maximum tasks number under a scene: 150.

    Maximum executive program under a task: 10.

    APP Load

    Maximum "Families" per app account: 20.

    Maximum devices per room: 50.

    Maximum "group set" per "home": 20.

    Maximum users that a "group set" can be shared with: 20.

    Maximum devices under a "group set": 100.

      If you have never done electrical work before then you need to consult an electrician. THESE LIGHTS ARE NOT UL LISTED FOR AMERICAN USE. These lights have connectors on them which i believe could cause a fire hazard down the road. Remove them and use wire nuts to splice the... See more
      If you have never done electrical work before then you need to consult an electrician. THESE LIGHTS ARE NOT UL LISTED FOR AMERICAN USE. These lights have connectors on them which i believe could cause a fire hazard down the road. Remove them and use wire nuts to splice the connections, then use to electrical tape to tape the splices. The holes you need can be drilled out with a 2 1/4 inch holesaw.

      I personally knew these lights would be a little on the unsafe side but knowing where the hazards are is key. I bought these to replace my fluorescent light over my sink and they work perfectly fine.
